name: Fake ma po tofu
ingredients:
- pork belly or shoulder: about 200g minced
- tofu: 1 carton about 300g
- garlic, ginger:
- sichuan peppers: 1 teapoon
- peas or spring onions:
- korean red paste: 1 teaspoon
- black bean: 1 cube
- salt. white pepper. sugar:
- sesame oil:
- soya sauce:
steps:
- put the kettle on
- grind sichuan peppers
- hot wok. add oil then garlic and ginger
- add red paste, sichuan peppers, black beans
- add minced pork and cook
- add tofu, add boiling water. simmer and cover
- season, salt, soya sauce, sugar, seasame oil
